Allows to create new proxy contact and execute a message call to the new proxy within one transaction.
 @author Stefan George - <stefan@gnosis.pm>
@dev Allows to retrieve the runtime code of a deployed Proxy. This can be used to check that the expected Proxy was deployed.
@dev Allows to retrieve the creation code used for the Proxy deployment. With this it is easily possible to calculate predicted address.

Allows to create new proxy contact and execute a message call to the new proxy within one transaction.
 @author Stefan George - <stefan@gnosis.pm>
@dev Allows to retrieve the runtime code of a deployed Proxy. This can be used to check that the expected Proxy was deployed.
@dev Allows to retrieve the creation code used for the Proxy deployment. With this it is easily possible to calculate predicted address.

calculateCreateProxyWithNonceAddress(add.details: Allows to get the address for a new proxy contact created via `createProxyWithNonce`      This method is only meant for address calculation purpose when you use an initializer that would revert,      therefore the response is returned with a revert. When calling this method set `from` to the address of the proxy factory.

params.initializer: Payload for message call sent to new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

params.data: Payload for message call sent to new proxy contract.

createProxyWithCallback(address,bytes,ui.details: Allows to create new proxy contact, execute a message call to the new proxy and call a specified callback within one transaction

params.callback: Callback that will be invoked after the new proxy contract has been successfully deployed and initialized.
params.initializer: Payload for message call sent to new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

createProxyWithNonce(address,bytes,uint2.details: Allows to create new proxy contact and execute a message call to the new proxy within one transaction.

params.initializer: Payload for message call sent to new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

proxyCreationCode().details: Allows to retrieve the creation code used for the Proxy deployment. With this it is easily possible to calculate predicted address.

proxyRuntimeCode().details: Allows to retrieve the runtime code of a deployed Proxy. This can be used to check that the expected Proxy was deployed.
